address1: Santa Cruz de la Zarza, nº 3
longBusinessSummary: Compañia Levantina de Edificacion y Obras Publicas, S.A., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the construction and public works businesses in Spain. It constructs homes and tourist apartments, industrial buildings, sport facilities, educational centers, and hospital buildings, penitentiary centers, pipelines, dams and reservoirs, roads, bridges, transfers, and urbanization, as well as irrigation modernization facilities; rehabilitates and restores emblematic buildings and monuments; develops residential centers, and geriatric centers and projects. The company also manages and administrates residential and day centers for the elderly; provides home help, data outsourcing, and engineering services; performs collection, public road signaling, personnel control services, etc.; and manages and operates data center infrastructure facilities, as well as offers administrative concession contracts for the removal of vehicles from the public highway. Compañia Levantina de Edificacion y Obras Publicas, S.A. was founded in 1926 and is based in Valencia, Spain.
longName: Compañia Levantina de Edificacion y Obras Publicas, S.A.
